Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.19,0:01:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹巴的興趣異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且相當下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.92,0:01:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是女孩子明知道這點\n還自願上他的當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎也是,拉莎拉也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.80,0:01:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連哈曼都是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.90,0:01:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是令人受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.20,0:01:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女人太現實了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.98,0:02:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十一話\n拉莎拉的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.69,0:02:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屬下真是不知情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒屬下的無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,史丹巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.36,0:02:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讓我以極有趣的方式\n觀賞了一般人的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.91,0:02:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本殖民地就等於小的庭院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.14,0:02:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屬下會親手把\n新亞加碼的人抓來給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會駕駛MS嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.53,0:02:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,我是暴發戶\n當然會駕駛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.08,0:02:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼多魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.37,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍一疏忽\n大家就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.98,0:03:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去見哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去見她幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.31,0:03:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一看就知道你很衰弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.04,0:03:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道是為什麼嗎?\n不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.52,0:03:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為之前我們的波動\n保護了捷度他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.96,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今那已超出我們的極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.50,0:03:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧\n我是保護光之族教養的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.48,0:03:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是要傳撥光的教義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.17,0:03:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.26,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題在於\n哈曼是來見捷度的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.93,0:03:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那捷度去見她便好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題沒那麼簡單啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?\n不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼和捷度在互相呼喚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度與哈曼對決就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要我做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.34,0:04:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於哈曼的原因\n捷度失去大家的信賴感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.13,0:04:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要去見她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.41,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.37,0:04:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會妨礙你的\n讓我一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能只讓姊姊去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.14,0:04:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.60,0:04:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你們\n拉莎拉,莫迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼莎拉莎\n跟拉莎拉不在的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.73,0:04:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已找遍艦內各個角落了\n就是找不到人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪也不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們三個人一起走的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.76,0:05:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢?\n我們不是不能進入殖民地嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.94,0:05:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹巴看上她們\n也許她們是被綁走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.71,0:05:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,新亞加碼會人手不足的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在指使我嗎?\n我是代理艦長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那更該留在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.45,0:05:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說話不要再吞吞吐吐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是被你鍛煉出來的,比查兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.55,0:05:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兄弟\n有個好東西,要不要買阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,我趕時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我算你便宜點,買吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.98,0:05:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說啊\n這商品很不錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是新亞加碼的船員吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.75,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓他們逃走,追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙\n不像哈曼的手下,不是軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是史丹巴的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你跑了這麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.09,0:07:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們是我的十三\n和十四號夫人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.15,0:07:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們喜歡年輕男人的\n你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算年輕男人,你也不合規格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.39,0:07:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要踩死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會算你便宜點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美女是應該帶美麗的寶物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別買了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.71,0:07:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.35,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我讓你當僊貝\n別逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了\n我的女人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉,拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙,竟然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.44,0:08:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛,是那時的...\n我要先采死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒有帶武器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用頭腦與身體就能贏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在香格里拉\n我們也能活下來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,你也要治療啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.73,0:09:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉更痛苦啊,不必管我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.09,0:09:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月月的人就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉\n拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.90,0:09:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉\n拉莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.41,0:09:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要跑到什麼時候啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問後面的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼辦法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.74,0:09:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正這麼打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.89,0:09:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我引開他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.31,0:09:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你能持續到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.41,0:10:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉,你到底想說什麼?\n你原本想對我說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.29,0:10:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可原諒,我絕不會原諒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不原諒她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.76,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?你想過來嗎?\n捷度.桑達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,不可以去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.48,0:11:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想再看到\n有人在我眼前死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.03,0:11:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你妹妹死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這全都是哈曼那女人的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.55,0:11:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的,哈曼是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但她也是個可悲的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.80,0:11:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是哈曼在冰冷的宇宙中受到委屈\n也不該詛咒地球的人們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.52,0:11:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我才說她可悲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.20,0:11:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎\n讓捷度去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.72,0:11:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是沒人原諒的話\n怨恨只會更擴大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.38,0:11:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼卡基.尼蓋爾格\n和殖民地接觸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.91,0:12:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感覺到你的存在了,哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要走,不要離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.71,0:12:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把人趕走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.13,0:12:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你...\n全因為你大家才會不幸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.77,0:12:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道我為何選擇\n以這方式和你見面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.80,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算知道\n拉莎拉也不會復活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜也不必那麼痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說你無法飛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.48,0:13:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟那些靈魂被重力吸引的人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別令我失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.87,0:13:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與我合作\n共創新人類的世紀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼是個可悲的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.28,0:13:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想妨礙我嗎?史丹巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那孩子使我失去了好的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這你不能插手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了女人?\n這個傭俗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.51,0:13:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,享受人生與個人原則是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快躲避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.08,0:13:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.79,0:14:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛MS,追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.30,0:14:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問我怎麼辦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是說\n要活用頭腦與身體嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就快活用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.52,0:14:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫伊萊當代理艦長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舊式機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還可以變形啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來的好,是誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.28,0:15:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,竟然偷襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個MS\n不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.13,0:15:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟上次的駕駛員不同\n太不成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.14,0:15:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ剛彈沒出動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.41,0:15:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有,哈曼大人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新吉翁新型MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.68,0:15:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會在這裏的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然偷偷攻擊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以用武器的話,這MS...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手,你想把殖民地打穿嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.76,0:15:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你才對啊\n幹什麼駕駛MS出動啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.50,0:15:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼在附近啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.04,0:15:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.48,0:15:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有在動腦,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在想辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地好像有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝你平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉一定會看守著你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,MK2可以出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.13,0:16:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通往市內的路線上魚雷掃清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.05,0:16:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.34,0:16:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別太勉強啊,莫迪\n拉莎拉會傷心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.96,0:16:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪駕駛剛彈MK2出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.32,0:17:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續壓制著他\n我要砍下他的頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.20,0:17:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人聽到停手就停手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MK2來了\n這次是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你吧,史丹巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.43,0:17:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得找出哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?先找人挑戰還想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.71,0:17:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹的好,比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渾蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你,我是絕不饒恕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這該死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真卑鄙,我只剩下一隻手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候你還囉唆什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.85,0:18:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停...手,停手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要替拉莎拉報仇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.63,0:19:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了\n拉莎拉,我成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.58,0:19:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文的手下嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.70,0:19:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了,謝謝你的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新吉翁的MS過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表示敵艦在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.36,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們也不能一直待在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好強行突擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.06,0:19:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我駕駛ZZ剛彈出擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.94,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.22,0:20:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連莫迪都那麼努力\n我怎麼能輸給他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,魚雷都掃清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.78,0:20:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思\n謝謝你的幫忙,魯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.26,0:20:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會以你們為榜樣\n好好努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.66,0:20:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝你們建立出更適合人類居住得殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.32,0:20:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰後一定要來玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.54,0:20:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.00,0:20:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有埋伏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.77,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來那MS只是來迎接哈曼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.01,0:20:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是拉莎拉在保護我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,一定是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.86,0:21:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.24,0:21:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭結束,請你一定要來見她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.75,0:21:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會去的\n不,我一定去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.47,0:21:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼與你有某種關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.99,0:21:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的\n今後的戰爭對你將成為大考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.99,0:21:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請別感到灰心沮喪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是許多人的希望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會謹記在心的,莎拉莎小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.22,0:21:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒什麼能力\n只能在一邊祈禱你們獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.22,0:21:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就麻煩你了\n我很需要你的祈禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向拉莎拉小姐的英靈默禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.14,0:22:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼是擁有使人不幸的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.80,0:23:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們利用礦山潛進了哈曼所在的SIDE 3
